snippet.title: War Hospital Gameplay Teaser - Future Games Show Gamescom 2021
snippet.description: Check out this teaser for Brave Lamb and Movie Games' War Hospital, a strategy game set in a field hospital in 1917. It's coming to PC, PlayStation and Xbox in 2022.
